==English==

===Etymology===
French

===Interjection===
'''voilà''' (''often'' '''[[voila]]!''')

# "Lo! There it is"

===Usage notes===
Since this is a French word spell-checkers flag it, so writers frequently misspell it [[viola]], [[wallah]], etc.  Also, American writers rarely have adequate training to know how to enter "à" using a US keyboard.

